default&#xa0;
defaultQ220default              defaultChair:default What rank should they be?  
defaultJeff Farrardefault: I do not think they should be a police officer, personally, but they are police officers in many forces.  
default&#xa0;
defaultQ136default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
