defaultQ257default              defaultPaul Flynn:default I am aware this is not unique, but these were special circumstances.  If we can go back into the very interesting story of crime figures in Gwent, I quoted earlier the year when one Welsh police force recorded a 3% increase and Gwent recorded a 15% reduction.  Damian Green said in Westminster Hall that in the period from June
